Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • vastus.sokoban.logic.Element
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Floor, Movable, Storage, Wall

    public abstract class Element
extends Object
    Abstract class describing elements in game. Element can be a player, box, storage or wall.
    Author:
    Juho Hautala
